* TL331 Single Differential Comparator Macro Model
* Pins: 1=IN- 2=GND 3=IN+ 4=OUT 5=VCC
*
* Parameters from datasheet:
*   VIO (input offset voltage): 2 mV typ
*   IIB (input bias current): -25 nA typ
*   AVD (open-loop gain): 200 V/mV = 200,000 V/V
*   VOL (output saturation): 150 mV @ IOL = 4 mA
*   ICC (supply current): 0.4 mA typ
*   Response time: ~1.3 us
*   Output: open collector NPN
*
* Architecture:
*   1. Differential input with offset
*   2. Gain stage with bandwidth limiting (f3dB ~ 120 kHz)
*   3. Output switch (open collector)
*
.SUBCKT TL331 1 2 3 4 5

* === Input Stage ===
* Input resistance for bias currents
RINP 3 2 40MEG
RINN 1 2 40MEG

* Differential error signal with offset voltage
EERR 10 2 VOL='(V(3,2) - V(1,2) - 0.002)'
RERR 10 2 1G

* === Gain Stage with Bandwidth Limiting ===
* Gain = 200,000 V/V
* Dominant pole at ~120 kHz (tau ~ 1.3 us)
* Using integrator for bandwidth control
EGAIN 20 2 VOL='V(10,2) * 200k'
RG 20 21 10k
CG 21 2 130p IC=0

* === Output Stage: Open Collector ===
* Comparator function: V(21) > 0 => IN+ > IN- => output LOW
* V(21) <= 0 => IN+ < IN- => output HIGH via external pullup

* Voltage-controlled switch with proper threshold
* Switch ON when V(21) > 0
SOUT 4 2 21 2 SWITCH_OUT
.MODEL SWITCH_OUT SW(VT=0 VH=0.01 RON=37.5 ROFF=10MEG)

* Protection diodes
DCLH 4 5 DID
DCLL 2 4 DID

* NPN model for input loading
RB 21 31 1k
QNPN 31 2 2 NPN_OUT
.MODEL NPN_OUT NPN (IS=1E-15 BF=100 NF=1 VAF=50
+   RB=50 RC=10 CJE=500f CJC=200f TF=1n TR=50n)

.MODEL DID D (IS=1e-14 N=1)

* === Supply Current ===
ICC_SRC 5 2 DC 0.4m

.ENDS TL331
